<i>I'm guilty.</i>

194
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:42,080
<i>I'm definitely guilty</i>.

195
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:45,070
<i>Why are you so particular about Kazuki Beer?</i>

196
00:13:45,070 --> 00:13:46,890
