220
00:15:06,950 --> 00:15:11,980
<i>How exactly am I supposed to face Nishijima Itsuka now?</i>

221
00:15:11,980 --> 00:15:14,550
<i>The one who changed me as a person...</i>

222
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:17,860
<i>You should try relying on others for a change,</i>

223
00:15:17,860 --> 00:15:19,320
<i>Mr. Caretaker.</i>

224
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:22,970
<i>is undoubtedly Nishijima Itsuka.</i>

225
00:15:22,970 --> 00:15:25,480
<i>From that moment on,</i>

226
00:15:26,220 --> 00:15:32,020
<i>she decided to dedicate everything to her job in order to get back at her client.</i>

227
00:15:32,020 --> 00:15:37,730
<i>Similarly so, the one who changed her, is none other than me.</i>

228
00:15:37,730 --> 00:15:39,710
